      <title>纽伯格警告称美国国债收益率将持续走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/neuberger-warns-of-sustained-move-higher-in-treasury-yields</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽伯格伯曼 (Neuberger Berman) 警告不要逢低买入美国国债，并表示近期的抛售可能是收益率“意外持续”走高的开始。]]></description>
